__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  UploadFileResponse:
    properties:
      fileId: optional<string>
      url: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  UploadMultipleFilesRequestMetadata:
    properties:
      title: optional<string>
      tags: optional<list<string>>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true
  UploadMultipleFilesResponse:
    properties:
      uploadedCount: optional<integer>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  UploadWithJsonRequestData:
    properties:
      name: optional<string>
      size: optional<integer>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true
  UploadWithJsonResponse:
    properties:
      success: optional<boolean>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    uploadFile:
      path: /upload
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        name: UploadFileRequest
        body:
          properties:
            file: file
            description: optional<string>
        content-type: multipart/form-data
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: UploadFileResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              fileId: fileId
              url: url
    uploadMultipleFiles:
      path: /upload-multiple
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        name: UploadMultipleFilesRequest
        body:
          properties:
            files: list<file>
            metadata: optional<UploadMultipleFilesRequestMetadata>
        content-type: multipart/form-data
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: UploadMultipleFilesResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              uploadedCount: 1
    uploadWithJson:
      path: /upload-with-json
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        name: UploadWithJsonRequest
        body:
          properties:
            file: file
            data: UploadWithJsonRequestData
        content-type: multipart/form-data
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: UploadWithJsonResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            data: {}
          response:
            body:
              success: true
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Multipart File Upload Edge Cases
